"CAjzZ\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable border\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched\" spellcheck=\"false\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\"><div>Work-family enrichment is the\npositive interaction between work and family domains. It is the extent to which\nexperiences in one role improve the quality of life in the other role.&nbsp;<span>Work-family enrichment has two types\nand three dimensions, which are instrumental and affective, development,\naffect, and capital respectively.</span></div></li><li class=\"\"><div><span><div>Workplace flexibility is the ability\nof workers to makes choices influencing the when, where, and for how long they\nare engaged in work-related activities. Workplace flexibility is delineated\ninto temporal and operational flexibility. Quality of work-life is defined as\nemployee satisfaction with a variety of needs through resources, activities,\nand outcomes stemming from participation in the workplace.</div></span></div></li><li class=\"\"><div><div>Employee loyalty is the deliberate\ncommitment of an employee to further the best interest of the employer even\nwhen doing so may demand to sacrifice some aspects of the employee's interest\nbeyond what is legally required of the employee's physical and moral\nduties. <span>Employee loyalty is divided into attitudinal and behavioral\nloyalty.</span></div></div></li><li class=\"\"><span><div>The nature of employee loyalty\nis reciprocity and contingent, in that loyal employees, don't stay forever, but\nthey deliver superior value to loyal customers while they are with the organization.&nbsp;<span>Employees are loyal to the\ncompany, their supervisors, their co-workers, and their jobs,</span></div></span></li><li class=\"\"><div><span>The reward for loyalty can be in the form of pay and added benefits. Also, recognition from a supervisor at the last two\nranks above an employee makes a meaningful, engaging difference in improving\nemployee morale.</span></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-isolate-scope ui-sortable ng-not-empty\"><li id=\"c51Ik\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Lesson Summary</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"CAjzZ\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable border\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched\" spellcheck=\"false\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\"><div>Work-family enrichment is the\npositive interaction between work and family domains. It is the extent to which\nexperiences in one role improve the quality of life in the other role.&nbsp;<span>Work-family enrichment has two types\nand three dimensions, which are instrumental and affective, development,\naffect, and capital respectively.</span></div></li><li class=\"\"><div><span><div>Workplace flexibility is the ability\nof workers to makes choices influencing the when, where, and for how long they\nare engaged in work-related activities. Workplace flexibility is delineated\ninto temporal and operational flexibility. Quality of work-life is defined as\nemployee satisfaction with a variety of needs through resources, activities,\nand outcomes stemming from participation in the workplace.</div></span></div></li><li class=\"\"><div><div>Employee loyalty is the deliberate\ncommitment of an employee to further the best interest of the employer even\nwhen doing so may demand to sacrifice some aspects of the employee's interest\nbeyond what is legally required of the employee's physical and moral\nduties. <span>Employee loyalty is divided into attitudinal and behavioral\nloyalty.</span></div></div></li><li class=\"\"><span><div>The nature of employee loyalty\nis reciprocity and contingent, in that loyal employees, don't stay forever, but\nthey deliver superior value to loyal customers while they are with the organization.&nbsp;<span>Employees are loyal to the\ncompany, their supervisors, their co-workers, and their jobs,</span></div></span></li><li class=\"\"><div><span>The reward for loyalty can be in the form of pay and added benefits. Also, recognition from a supervisor at the last two\nranks above an employee makes a meaningful, engaging difference in improving\nemployee morale.</span></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n"]}